snippet.title: Диана открывает Календарь Diana Opens Advent Calendar "Olaf's Frozen Adventure"
snippet.description:
We opened all surprises at once to start playing with toys. Each window easily be popped out and just take the surprise figure inside! We liked that the figures are all high-quality, the details are real good that the makers really captured the different expressions of Olaf. Diana was very interesting to discover the surprises and fun toys to play.

Diana Opens Advent Calendar with Barbie doll surprise for kids video
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aq7zISO7PYE
